'''热带风暴爱丽丝'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Alice}}）是1953年5月底到6月初吹袭[[中美洲|中美洲]]、[[古巴|古巴]]和[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]的罕见[[淡季大西洋热带气旋名单|淡季]]热带气旋，也是有纪录以来第一个以[[女性人名|女性人名]]命名的[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]。气旋于5月25日在西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]成型，移动路线在中美洲上空形成大规模环路。风暴从古巴西部上空经过并降下暴雨，可能导致多人溺毙。接下来气旋的行动路径又在[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]形成环状，在此期间达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]110公里的最高强度，然后逐渐减弱，于6月6日吹袭[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]西北狭长地带。该州出现暴雨，但没有受到严重破坏。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Alice 1953 track.png}}
1953年5至6月，[[墨西哥|墨西哥]]和[[中美洲|中美洲]]上空存在持续时间异常长久的上层[[低气压|低气压区]]。5月25日，[[尼加拉瓜|尼加拉瓜]]以东海域发展出弱暖芯[[大气环流|下层环流]]。这片天气系统围绕上层低气压区移动，推动低气压区朝西北前进，之后又以弧形路线南下，经过[[洪都拉斯|洪都拉斯]]和中美洲。系统在陆地上空减弱，但在西[[加勒比海|加勒比海]]上空又重新强化，于5月31日以每小时80公里风速的热带风暴强度进入[[古巴|古巴]]西部上空。<ref name="mwr">{{cite report | author = Grady Norton | work = Miami Weather Bureau Office | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | year = 1953 | title = Hurricanes of 1953 | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | archivedate = 2016-03-03 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160303171215/http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/081/mwr-081-12-0388.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://docs.lib.noaa.gov/rescue/mwr/081/mwr-081-12-0388.pdf | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | date =  }}</ref>不过，气象机构直到6月1日风暴进入[[墨西哥湾|墨西哥湾]]时才开始针对爱丽丝发布公告<ref name="timesdaily">{{cite web | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | newspaper = The Florence Times | publisher = Google News Archive | date = 1953-06-01 | title = Season's First Storm Develops in Gulf as Winds Increase Rate | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=pvsrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pMYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4365,5752516&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210918112644/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=pvsrAAAAIBAJ&sjid=pMYEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4365,5752516&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en }}</ref>。

气旋获命名的同时，[[飓风猎人|飓风猎人]]侦察机测得的风速约为每小时105公里，爱丽丝随后的移动路线在古巴西北近海形成又一个圆环<ref name="mwr" />。受[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]近海的[[冷锋|冷锋]]影响，系统很快减弱至热带风暴标准下限<ref>{{cite web | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | publisher = Google News Archive | date = 1953-06-03 | title = Cold Gulf Air Cools 'Cane Alice | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HNwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1463,235999&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201219182323/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HNwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1463%2C235999&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。风暴消退幅度很大，气象部门甚至停发公告，迈阿密气象局气象学家詹姆斯·乔治（{{lang|en|James George}}）对此表示：“反正也没什么危险<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = Palm Beach Post | author = Staff Writer | publisher = Google News Archive | date = 1953-06-03 | title = Storm 'Alice' Fizzles in Gulf | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HNwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1463,235999&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201219182323/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=HNwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1463%2C235999&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。”再度从古巴近海经过后，爱丽丝转向西北并开始重新增强。6月5日，侦察机估计中心东北方向短暂出现时速110至120公里的强风，气压低至997[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，29.4[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]），这也是风暴的最高强度。气旋在逼近[[佛罗里达半岛|佛罗里达半岛]]期间再度减弱，最终于6月6日以热带风暴强度下限在[[巴拿马市海滩_(佛罗里达州)|巴拿马市海滩]]以西不远处[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]，此后不久便完全消散。<ref name="mwr" />

== 影响和纪录 ==
[[File:Alice_1953_rainfall.png|thumb]]

风暴行进至古巴西部附近时降下暴雨，为当地持续九个月之久的干旱划上句点。降水引发洪灾，报导称当地有多人淹死，但消息没有得到确认。<ref name="mwr" />

[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始针对风暴发布公告的同时向[[基韦斯特_(佛罗里达州)|基韦斯特]]至[[塔彭斯普林斯|塔彭斯普林斯]]间的佛罗里达州西海岸发布风暴警告；与此同时，该机构还向[[棕榈滩|棕榈滩]]及其南侧的佛罗里达东海岸地区发布小型船只警告<ref name="timesdaily" />。爱丽丝在该州产生暴雨，佛罗里达中部的[[普莱西德湖_(佛罗里达州)|普莱西德湖]]降水最多，达342毫米<ref name="Florida Rain">{{cite book | last1 = Roth | first1 = David M | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304062338/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcflorida.html | author2 = Hydrometeorological Prediction Center | year = 2012 | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Point Maxima | publisher = United States National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration's National Weather Service | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall in Florida | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcflorida.html | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，该州旱情因此缓解<ref name="mwr" />。佛罗里达西北狭长地带沿线多个空军和海军基地的工作人员将飞机固定，基地没有发布撤离令，受到的影响以小雨为主<ref>{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = Sarasota Herald-Tribune | publisher = Google News Archive | date = 1953-06-07 | title = Florida Storm Buffets Beaches | accessdate = 2010-01-05 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=INwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3705,819192&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | archive-date = 2021-09-18 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210918112642/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=INwbAAAAIBAJ&sjid=w2QEAAAAIBAJ&pg=3705,819192&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en }}</ref>。佛罗里达州的损失情况缺乏统计和报导<ref name="mwr" />。

1950至1952年间的大西洋飓风是用[[美国陆军/海军联合拼音字母|美国陆军/海军联合拼音字母]]命名。1953年大西洋飓风季开始前，气象机构变更命名法，改为使用女性人名，“爱丽丝”（{{lang|en|Alice}}）便是此次调整后使用的第一个名字<ref>{{cite news | agency = United Press International | newspaper = Reading Eagle | date = 1953-06-01 | title = Tropical Storm Whips Cuban Coast | publisher = Google News Archive | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=EMgtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3JsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1259,12022&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | archive-date = 2020-12-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201219182413/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=EMgtAAAAIBAJ&sjid=3JsFAAAAIBAJ&pg=1259%2C12022&dq=tropical+storm+alice&hl=en | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此后一直到1979年，[[北大西洋热带气旋|北大西洋热带气旋]]才开始在命名时采用男性人名<ref name="HURDAT">{{cite report | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | year = 2009 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | accessdate = 2016-09-29 | title = Easy-to-Read HURDAT 1851–2008 | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305031132/http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | deadurl = no | url = http://www.aoml.noaa.gov/hrd/hurdat/easyread-2009.html | date =  }}</ref>。名称“爱丽丝”之后在1954年[[1954年6月飓风爱丽丝|6月]]和[[1954年12月飓风爱丽丝|12月]]两度使用，还曾在1973年使用<ref name="HURDAT" />。
